<custom_item>
  type             : AUDIT_XML
  description      : "PANW-IP-000041 - The Palo Alto Networks security platform must protect against or limit the effects of known and unknown types of Denial of Service (DoS) attacks by employing rate-based attack prevention behavior analysis (traffic thresholds) - DoS Protection Policy"
